{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2148","airdate":"1549998000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Originals and their best covers","blurb":"Hello Folks,\n\nSince we had a lot of SID requests last week, we will try a new concept: Ask for an original SID or Amiga module that has an existing remix! We will play the original first and then the best rated remix of it from RKO or Amigaremix.com!\n\nAnd don't forget - Sunday is the ROTY Awards Show. \nWe are already warming up for that too :) \n\nJoin the fun and SLAY tuned!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Originals and their best covers","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 12th February, 2019<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2146","airdate":"1550394000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PmpVsBionicBoots","blurb":"I'm going to talk a bit about bionic boots and how a video about them is making me sad.\n\nThen I'm also going to talk a bit more about the Fyre festival.\n\nYou will either listen, watch, both, or neither. The choice is yours!\n\nGazoo","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PmpVsBionicBoots","nice_airdate":"Sunday 17th February, 2019<br \/>at 10:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2145","airdate":"1550422800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Remix64.com","showname":"Remixer of the Year Awards 2018","blurb":"The time has come to celebrate and acknowledge the remixers' work in the C64 and Amiga community by presenting the yearly ROTY Awards, as voted by the users at www.remix64.com. This year it's SLAY Radio's turn to give out the awards and give you a run-down of what happened in 2018.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Remix64.com<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Remixer of the Year Awards 2018","nice_airdate":"Sunday 17th February, 2019<br \/>at 18:00 USRT"}]}